Profile

MORE
Salesforce, Inc. is a provider of customer relationship management (CRM) technology. The Company helps organizations of any size reimagine their business for the world of artificial intelligence (AI). With Agentforce, its platform, organizations can bring humans together with agents to drive customer success powered by AI, data, and action. With the Salesforce platform, the Company delivers a single source of truth, connecting customer data with integrated AI across systems...

Chairman of the Board, Chief Executive Officer, Co-Founder
